Yocto layer for NXP DataPlane
===================================

Dependencies
------------
QorIQ SDK 2.0 Release ISOs:
QorIQ-SDK-V2.0-SOURCE-20160527-yocto.iso
QorIQ-SDK-V2.0-AARCH64-CACHE-20160527-yocto.iso

Build Images
------------
Download and Install the SDK ISOs from:
http://www.nxp.com/products/software-and-tools/run-time-software/linux-sdk/linux-sdk-for-qoriq-processors:SDKLINUX

Download this yocto layer into following ISO installation folder:
<path>/QorIQ-SDK-V2.0-20160527-yocto/sources/

Setup the build environment:
  $ . ./fsl-setup-env -m <machine>

Build the kernelitb:
  $ bitbake fsl-image-kernelitb 
